{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ec6a5110ce","title":"给李介侯的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"176b433924","index":0,"year":1951,"month":4,"day":2,"articleId":"ec6a5110ce"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji30","name":"毛泽东全集第30卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/30-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji30":{"comments":[{"id":"d344a15884","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"ec6a5110ce","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"徐冰（1903-1972），河北南官人。当时任中共中央统战部副部长。"},{"id":"87b9f663f5","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"ec6a5110ce","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这里有误，应该是李介候妹妹的女儿（宋明）。李介侯在1951年3月28日给毛泽东的信中说：我现在中国进口公司机械科负责，我家着已来到北京。北京方面的生活完满地解决了，一切都是由于你的帮助。可是，我父亲（即李激清）把被人遗弃的我妹妹的女儿宋明，也交我家卷带到北京。我父亲来信请求你替她找一个免费的中学读书。拟请设法进入产科、护士等免费学校或半工半读的学校读书。"}],"contents":[{"id":"c6b81a80e7","type":"title","text":"给李介侯的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"ec6a5110ce"},{"id":"d344a15884","type":"paragraph","text":"介侯兄：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"ec6a5110ce"},{"id":"87b9f663f5","type":"paragraph","text":"请持此信去统战部找徐冰同志，或其他同志，和他商量是否有办法为你妹妹以找一个免费的或半工半读的学校，如产科、护士或其他学校。我想，只要有可能，是应当替她解决学习和工作问题的。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"ec6a5110ce"},{"id":"86a4308a44","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"ec6a5110ce"},{"id":"13e042bdee","type":"paragraph","text":"四月二日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"ec6a5110ce"}],"page":{"id":"a35b9e98bf","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"ec6a5110ce","start":213,"end":213}}}},"__N_SSG":true}